{"tid":21820,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"被問到有否合作空間 梁頌恆：熱普城欠缺論述、計劃","createTime":"2016-12-04T05:40:17.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-04T07:21:16.000Z","uid":34884,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ea09f05752033dbfa597da949b307da6c9398bc7","tid":21820,"uid":34884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T05:40:17.000Z","msg":"//不過，青政現時有兩個議席，似乎更不怕只得一席的熱普城和被游蕙禎踢走的黃毓民，對於兩個組織有否合作空間，梁反指熱普城應先釐清論述，青政才可作下一步判斷，「佢哋嘅說法喺近半年已經轉咗幾次，甚至我其中一位競爭對手（熱普城陳云根）講到今次已經係一次公投，呢個係佢哋陣營所講嘅，咁我依家要跟邊一套計劃？要等佢哋有整個計劃先會有下一步。」//&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://nextplus.nextmedia.com/news/latest/20160910/426110\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Flatest%2F20160910%2F426110&d=2%2FmELneL9Q%2Bp6j2sEUyr00sIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=57a48095\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Flatest%2F20160910%2F426110&h=64227dbe\" target=\"_blank\">http://nextplus.nextmedia.com/news/latest/20160910/426110</a>"},{"pid":"298e459d20a006aaeebdcf4f4097355a16340449","tid":21820,"uid":34884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T05:42:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1df852b4555af190fcbec232c910f30f03fa493","tid":21820,"uid":22318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T05:44:17.000Z","msg":"&gt;0"},{"pid":"6911029acdff49ff30128ec5b4105bd33f92ec84","tid":21820,"uid":34884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T05:47:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28ee7ad209a12252268117a5ffae40265a6ebe0a","tid":21820,"uid":46804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T05:59:42.000Z","msg":"自大"},{"pid":"e9286360446a87693c84a10dfa6a117b927d78b2","tid":21820,"uid":34884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T06:11:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>自大</blo